title: Paadu Nilave
subTitle: When Balakrishnan, a police constable, expresses his love to a renowned singer, she rejects his advances. Balakrishnan feels insulted and decides to exact revenge on her.

title: Enakkaga Kaathiru
subTitle: Vijay and Chandar are best friends who live by tricking other people. However, an unexpected death takes a tragic toll on their relationship.

title: Enga Ooru Rasathi
subTitle: A mischievous girl falls in love with Azhagu, a young tailor of the village. However, her peaceful life turns chaotic when she starts working for Vishalum.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Maasilamani
subTitle: Maasilamani falls in love with a woman, Divya, who dislikes him. Trouble ensues when he concocts an elaborate story about his lookalike to win her heart.

title: Anegan

title: Vasool Raja MBBS
subTitle: A goon, Rajaraman, enrols himself in a medical college to fulfil his father's dream. He defies the college rules and creates problems for Dr Vishwanathan.

title: Dharma Durai
subTitle: Dharmadurai, a heartbroken doctor, turns to alcohol and becomes the source of embarrassment for his family. However, a meeting with an old friend changes his life for good.

title: Naan E
subTitle: Nani loves Bindu but is killed by a jealous businessman, Sudeep, who lusts over Bindu. Nani is reincarnated as a fly and decides to avenge his death and make Sudeep's life a living hell.

title: Goa
subTitle: Three mischievous young men escape their chaotic village life to Goa, chasing dreams of marrying wealthy foreign women, only to find out that it's easier said than done.

title: Suryavamsam
subTitle: Sakthivel, an influential man, is upset with his son Chinnarasu's careless attitude. He is further infuriated when Chinnarasu suddenly refuses to marry his cousin, Gowri.

title: London
